The '''Iranian Parliament Committee on Energy''' ({{lang-fa|کمیسیون انرژی مجلس شورای اسلامی}}), or Energy Committee is a standing committee of the [[Islamic Consultative Assembly]] of Representatives. The Parliament Committee on Energy has general Oil, gas, electricity, water and electric dams and power plants, nuclear power and renewable energy and it can recommend funding appropriations for various governmental agencies, programs, and activities, as defined by House rules.
