kelid=DMF20120805_00247922&word=thetis |title=Universiteit haalt afval kernreactor weg |first=Bert |last=Staes|language=Dutch|journal=standaard.be |date=6 August 2012 |accessdate=7 August 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Thetis van UGent is eerste gedeclasseerde reactor|url=https://www.sckcen.be/nl/News/20160225_UGent_Thetis|accessdate=25 March 2018|author=SCK•CEN}}</ref>
