The [[Bayer designation]] '''Tau Arietis''' (τ Ari, τ Arietis) is shared by two [[star system]]s, in the [[constellation]] [[Aries (constellation)|Aries]]: * [[Tau1 Arietis|τ<sup>1</sup> Arietis]] * [[Tau2 Arietis|τ<sup>2</sup> Arietis]] They are separated by 0.54°.
{{SIA|astronomical objects}}
[[Category:Aries (constellation)]] [[Category:Bayer objects|Arietis, Tau]]
